Here are the extracted sentences that meet the criteria:

NCT-501 inhibits hALDHl A1 with IC50 of 40 nM.
NCT-501 typically shows better selectivity over other ALDH isozymes and other dehydrogenases (hALDHlBl, hALDEBAl, and hALDH2, IC50 >57 mM).
4-Diethylaminobenzaldehyde is a reversible aldehyde dehydrogenases (ALDHs) inhibitor, with a Ki of 4 nM for ALDHl.
4-Diethylaminobenzaldehyde displays potent anti -androgenic effect (IC50= 1.71mM).
Daidzin directly inhibits mitochondrial aldehyde dehydrogenase 2 (IC50 = 80 nM) and is an effective anti-dipsotropic isoflavone.
CM10 is a potent and selective aldehyde dehydrogenase 1A family inhibitor (ALDHlAi), with IC50s of 1700, 740, and 640 nM for ALDHl Al, ALDHl A2, and ALDHl A3, respectively.
EN40 is a potent, selective aldehyde dehydrogenase 3A1 (ALDH3A1) inhibitor as a covalent ligand, exhibits an IC50 value of 2 mM.
CVT-10216 is a highly selective, reversible aldehyde dehydrogenase-2 (ALDH-2) inhibitor with an IC50 of 29 nM.
CVT-10216 also has inhibitory effect of ALDH-1 with an IC50 of 1.3 mM.
